===Etymology===
From {{term||religiōn-}}, the stem of the {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|religio|religiō|scrupulousness”, “pious misgivings”, “superstition”, “conscientiousness”, “sanctity”, “an object of veneration”, “cult-observance”, “reverence|lang=la}}, from {{term|religo|religō|I bind back or behind|lang=la}}, from {{term|re|lang=la}} + {{term|ligo|ligō|I tie, bind, or bandage|lang=la}}.

===Pronunciation===
